name: FF Milo (iOS13)
author: Evelyn (ev_ynw)
description:
Normal size. Install 'FF Milo_85%' for smaller character size.

Only compatible on iOS13. Separate package for iOS14 is available.

Installed to: /Library/Themes/[fontname].theme/

Apply with SnowBoard. Package name = Fonts.

Need help? Link to tutorials in my pinned tweet
